# Production Deployment Checklist

## Pre-Deployment
- [ ] **Frontend Build**: `npm run build` succeeds without errors
- [ ] **TypeScript**: All TS errors resolved
- [ ] **Backend Health**: `curl https://backend-production-80f6.up.railway.app/health`
- [ ] **Database**: Prisma migrations applied on Railway
- [ ] **Environment**: `VITE_API_BASE` set correctly in Netlify

## Frontend Deployment (Netlify)
- [ ] **Build Command**: `npm run build`
- [ ] **Publish Directory**: `dist`
- [ ] **Environment Variables**: `VITE_API_BASE=https://backend-production-80f6.up.railway.app`
- [ ] **Deploy Trigger**: Manual or automatic from Git
- [ ] **Domain**: https://ubiquitous-sherbet-b4f6bf.netlify.app/

## Backend Deployment (Railway)
- [ ] **Service**: Backend service active
- [ ] **Database**: PostgreSQL service connected
- [ ] **Environment**: `DATABASE_URL` set correctly
- [ ] **Health Check**: Backend responds to `/health`
- [ ] **API Endpoints**: All endpoints functional

## Post-Deployment Testing
- [ ] **Frontend Loads**: Site accessible without errors
- [ ] **File Upload**: CSV upload works end-to-end
- [ ] **Data Persistence**: Uploaded files appear in database
- [ ] **Cross-Device**: Data visible from different devices
- [ ] **API Integration**: Frontend successfully calls backend

## Monitoring
- [ ] **Error Logs**: Check Netlify and Railway logs
- [ ] **Performance**: Monitor response times
- [ ] **Database**: Verify data integrity
- [ ] **Uptime**: Ensure services remain available

## Rollback Plan
- [ ] **Previous Version**: Keep previous deployment as backup
- [ ] **Database Backup**: Regular PostgreSQL backups
- [ ] **Quick Revert**: Ability to rollback to working version
